{"tid":1755338,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黎明行動] 短暫修正","createTime":"2019-11-25T14:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T15:12:58.000Z","uid":81236,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e851e6237c9ff6149260b3b896ce5d458371497e","tid":1755338,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:04:01.000Z","msg":"大家記唔記得黎明行動係為左咩？<br />\n<br />\n係為左<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">罷工</span></span><br />\n<br />\n借助塞鐵同路幫助一班唔想罷工既人都罷埋一份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經過今次區選<br />\n<br />\n扣除老人院、蛇齋餅枕鐵票<br />\n<br />\n單以18歲有上班能力既人計<br />\n<br />\n分分有接近75-80%<br />\n<br />\n但罷工係一個全港性既囚徒困境遊戲<br />\n可參閱下文<br />\n<br />\n全港大罷工係史上最大型的囚徒困境遊戲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1698589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1698589</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我地唔可能唔理果20-25%<br />\n<br />\n所以最佳做法做係搵埋佢地加入，俾更多訊息佢哋指導<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我敢講早上搭車搭鐵返工既無20%知道已經有不同組別既工會成立，準備組織全港性既罷工</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人返工既動力係源自：<br />\n執輸行頭，慘過敗家<br />\n<br />\n全面及針對不同行業工會組織宣傳<br />\n例如向運輸業既司機派傳單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">推廣加入工會係對打工仔多一份保障</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">加入左先一定無輸，唔加入反而有機會蝕底</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而最佳接觸打工仔既時間就係返工時段同埋和你lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於返工時段進行工會組織宣傳係一定有效過囉單單網上宣傳<br />\n同時製作文宣宣傳政府漠視市民訴求同埋警暴<br />\n流水式咁派同宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借助今次廣告界一連五日既大罷工<br />\n宣傳工會罷工係香港唔係無可能<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">每多一個渠道知道有罷工行動<br />\n<br />\n對罷工同被罷工既抗拒性就會愈低<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n至於比大眾入屋方法可能要靠下文宣手足<br />\n<br />\n十分願意係地鐵站巴士站同埋公司派<br />\n<br />\n抗爭有機會係長期，做好兩手準備對抗極權"},{"pid":"fc790b7574635e732eebc102c63a7cffe623a283","tid":1755338,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4794cead667297ed0119e2acaa6ae60dbfa4e9df","tid":1755338,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:04:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ef53651bb8cf1825885376a0415238dd06e4810","tid":1755338,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:06:14.000Z","msg":"係政府逼到唔聽民意<br />\n<br />\n市民先要組織罷工<br />\n<br />\n最好保障自己嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n就係加入公會<br />\n<br />\n參與罷工行動<br />\n<br />\n呢個好重要<br />\n<br />\n錯既係政府"},{"pid":"87c2a3f5ea623146e55b5af82996ba4cc05f24eb","tid":1755338,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b12c9114532e0a47e9710a9ac458071c06bb43dd","tid":1755338,"uid":156791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:09:07.000Z","msg":"搞工會好過塞鐵"},{"pid":"6ab60dc0141b1036ba0d586b33401ac4a71467bd","tid":1755338,"uid":291203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:10:18.000Z","msg":"搞工會，推<br />\n<br />\n真春袋&middot;無人提？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755334</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2f90f2a6eadf8d51ed9a7aae2702a9c58a994164","tid":1755338,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b12c9114532e0a47e9710a9ac458071c06bb43dd","tid":1755338,"uid":156791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:09:07.000Z","msg":"搞工會好過塞鐵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:13:03.000Z","msg":"要時間組織"},{"pid":"2a15ed0b22e81fae2ae9e38f5acd7e4781870f66","tid":1755338,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:15:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"034fc37679cdcb09ebb0310863003e0db99dfd81","tid":1755338,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid